---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact | TSA Monster"
  description="Get in touch with TSA Monster — for editorial questions, review requests, press inquiries, or corrections. We read every email and respond within a few business days."
>
  <main class="flex-1 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
      <h1 class="font-display">Contact</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        We're a small team, but we read every email. Whether you've spotted an error, want to
        discuss a review, or have a product you think deserves coverage — reach out.
      </p>

      <h2>Editorial Inquiries</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about our content, methodology, or a specific review:
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@tsa.monster" class="text-brand font-semibold">hello@tsa.monster</a>
      </p>
      <p>
        We aim to respond within 2–3 business days. For factual corrections, please include the
        URL of the article in question and the specific claim you believe is inaccurate — we take
        corrections seriously and will update the record if the evidence supports it.
      </p>

      <h2>Review Requests</h2>
      <p>
        If you represent a brand or product and would like us to consider a product for review,
        you're welcome to reach out at the address above. A few things worth knowing upfront:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          We only review products that fit our current editorial scope: kitchen tools, outdoor gear,
          home essentials, and beauty products.
        </li>
        <li>
          Receiving a product for review does not guarantee publication, and it does not guarantee
          a positive review. We disclose when a product was provided by a brand.
        </li>
        <li>
          We do not accept payment for editorial coverage. Sponsored content, if ever published,
          will be labeled explicitly.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Press Inquiries</h2>
      <p>
        For media inquiries, interview requests, or press-related questions, email us at the
        address above with "Press" in the subject line. We'll route it to the right person.
      </p>

      <h2>Privacy and Affiliate Questions</h2>
      <p>
        For questions about how we handle data or how our affiliate relationships work, our{' '}
        <a href="/en/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a> and{' '}
        <a href="/en/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> pages cover most scenarios.
        If they don't answer your question, email us at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:hello@tsa.monster">hello@tsa.monster</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
